# Tests de l'API d'administration SAMAFOOT
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api

### 1. Connexion du Super Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@samafoot.sn",
    "password": "admin123"
}

### 2. Connexion de l'Editor
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "editor@samafoot.sn",
    "password": "editor123"
}

### 3. Connexion du Manager
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "manager@samafoot.sn",
    "password": "manager123"
}

### 4. Récupérer les informations du profil (après connexion)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/admin/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Changer le mot de passe
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/admin/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "current_password": "admin123",
    "new_password": "newpassword123",
    "new_password_confirmation": "newpassword123"
}

### 6. Créer un nouvel administrateur (Super Admin seulement)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/admin/create
Authorization: Bearer {{super_admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Nouvel Admin Test",
    "email": "test@samafoot.sn",
    "password": "test123",
    "password_confirmation": "test123",
    "role": "admin"
}

### 7. Lister tous les administrateurs (Super Admin seulement)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/admin/list
Authorization: Bearer {{super_admin_token}}

### 8. Déconnexion
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/admin/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
